snippet.title: Goiken Muyou: Anarchy in the NIPPON | Aya Katsuragi | Saturn
snippet.description:
Sega Saturn test recording in OBS with custom color correction, sharpness and LUT.
SUBSCRIBE ► http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7wkTM_h3HsXb1EsVK6Imbw?sub_confirmation=1 
AND FOLLOW ME DOWN THE RABBIT HOLE!

Note: "I've given myself more health and my opponents less health, so as not to waste 15 minutes or more alone on the last two stages."
